        "body": "### Problem\r\nThe \"Return to Tactical Overview\" button in the `TrackerResultsPage` component was redirecting users to the wrong destination. This broke the navigation flow and prevented users from returning to the Contribution Analyzer page as intended.\r\n\r\n### Root Cause\r\nThe button's `onClick` handler had incorrect routing logic, causing it to navigate to an unexpected URL instead of the Contribution Analyzer page.\r\n\r\n### Solution\r\n✅ Updated the button's click handler to correctly route to `/opensource/track` (Contribution Analyzer)  \r\n✅ Ensured the button label accurately reflects its destination  \r\n✅ Maintained consistent styling and visual appearance  \r\n\r\n### Changes Made\r\n- **File Modified:** `devtrack/frontend/src/app/opensource/track/[username]/page.tsx`\r\n- **Component:** `TrackerResultsPage`\r\n- Updated `onClick` handler from incorrect route to correct destination\r\n- Button now properly navigates to the Contribution Analyzer page\r\n\r\n### Testing\r\n- ✅ Verified button navigation works correctly\r\n- ✅ User is routed to the intended Contribution Analyzer page\r\n- ✅ No console errors or warnings\r\n- ✅ Button styling and appearance unchanged\r\n- ✅ No impact to other page components\r\n\r\n### Impact\r\n- **Type:** Bug Fix\r\n- **Scope:** Small (single component, focused change)\r\n- **Breaking Changes:** None\r\n- **User Impact:** Users can now correctly return to Contribution Analyzer from Tracker Results\r\n\r\n### Related Issues\r\nCloses #10 \r\n\r\n---\r\n**Ready for review! 🚀**",
